contentrichtext.text: '''JIC''' is a [[three-letter abbreviation]] with multiple meanings, as described below: * [[John Innes Centre]] * [[Joint Intelligence Center]] * [[Joint Industrial Council]] * [[Incident Command System#Facilities|Joint Information Center]] * [[Jordan Insurance Company]] * [[Jubail_Industrial_College|Jubail Industrial College, Saudi Arabia]] * [[Jubilee International Church]] * [[Just_in_Case|Just in Case (Novel)]] * [[Just_in_case|Just in case (Manufacturing)]] * "just in case" in [[internet slang]] * ''[[Communist Left Youth|Juventud de Izquierda Comunista]]'' * [[UK Joint Intelligence Committee]] * [[JIC fitting|JIC tubing fitting]] {{disambiguation}}
